milestones.description: Dean Minors and Steven Outerbridge's 30-run partnership is BMUDA's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 28 between Steven Outerbridge and Kwame Tucker
Dean Minors has broken the record for most sixes (7) in ODIs for BMUDA, going past Romaine's 5
Mukuddem has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (9) for BMUDA, going past Romaine

stories.title: Dhaniram blasts Canada home
stories.subTitle: Bermuda v Canada, Tri-series, 2nd match
stories.summary: A fine partnership of 91 in 13 overs between Ashish Bagai and Sunil Dhaniram enabled Canada to bounce straight back from their defeat against Netherlands as they overturned Bermuda by five wickets at Potchefstroom
